sourcesContent: import mainApi from "../mainApi";    export default {        name: "AppsSettings",        data: function () {            return {                domains: [],                appName: "",                headers: [                    {                        text: 'Applications',                        align: 'left',                        sortable: false,                        value: 'name'                    },                    { text: 'Id', value: 'Id'},                    { text: 'Status', value: 'Status' },                    { text: 'Creation', value: 'Creation' },                    { text: 'Settings', value: 'Settings' }                ],            }        },        created() {            mainApi().get('/apps/' + this.$route.params.name + '/domains', {})                .then(response => {                    this.domains = response.data.domains;                    console.log(this.domains);                }).catch(e => {                console.log(e);            })        }    }
